# Project overview

- **Path:** `ecommerce-nextjs/` (lowercase folder at repo root)
- **Stack:** Next.js 16 App Router, Convex (realtime), shadcn/ui + Tailwind v4, TypeScript strict
- **Legacy reference:** React app in `../client/` — port behavior, do not break Convex patterns

## Commands

- Dev: `npm run dev` (Next.js + `convex dev`)
- Seed: `npm run seed`
- Add UI: `npm run ui:add <component>` or `npx shadcn@latest add <name>`

## Providers

- `ShadcnProviders` — theme, tooltips, Sonner toasts (root layout)
- `AppProviders` — Convex, cart/filter context (shop layout)
